  "tosSection4Intro": "You agree NOT to:",
  "tosSection4Bullet1": "Use the Service for any unlawful purpose;",
  "tosSection4Bullet2": "Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or disassemble the app;",
  "tosSection4Bullet3": "Upload content that is malicious, fraudulent, or violates intellectual property rights;",
  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access data belonging to Altro users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "Use the Service to send unsolicited communications or spam.",
  "tosSection5Title": "Subscriptions & Payments",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EEnterprise plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tTermini",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or Annulla your subscription at any Ora through your platform's account sImpostazioni",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will non apply to your current billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "Your Data",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Salute data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Privacy Policy, which is incorporated into these Termini by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Esporta your data at any Ora via the in-app Esporta feature, and you may permanently Elimina your account and Tutti associated data via Impostazioni → Elimina Account.",
